@dsymonds Certainly. Likewise `gofmt` is an wonderful tool that addresses a social issue. 

> "I've found gofmt a great antidote to senior devs who want all code formatted in their style." - @dgryski

It so happens that gofmt address a social issue in large companies and in open source projects. I'm not sure if aliases are as equally applicable to both, but I only just read the proposal. Still thinking.
